### get server health
GET http://localhost:5118/health


### get all games
GET http://localhost:5118/games

### Get by id
GET http://localhost:5118/games/1

### create a new game
POST http://localhost:5118/games
Content - Type: application / json

{
  "name" : "Fire",
   "genreId" : 1,
    "price" : 4.99,
    "releaseDate" : "2020-12-24"
}

### update a game
PUT http://localhost:5118/games/1
Content - Type: application / json

{
  "name" : "Black Ops 2",
   "genreId" : 2,
   "price" : 4.99,
   "releaseDate" : "2020-12-24"
}
### delet a game
DELETE http://localhost:5118/games/1


